-- Reserve Bank Says India's Double-Digit Inflation Within Its Projection
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-06-17T03:47:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/reserve-bank-says-india-s-double-digit-inflation-within-its-projection.html

          
          
             Reserve Bank Deputy Governor K.C.
Chakrabarty said double-digit inflation in India is within the
projection of the central bank. He was speaking to reporters in
Mumbai today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
